'''贝妮代塔·皮拉托'''（{{lang-it|Benedetta Pilato}}，{{bd|2005年|1月28日||}}）生于塔兰托，是一名意大利女子游泳运动员，主攻蛙泳<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.federnuoto.it/home/nuoto/azzurri-nuoto/scheda/340:Benedetta_Pilato.html|script-title=it:Benedetta Pilato|work={{lang|it|Federazione Italiana Nuoto}}|accessdate=2020-12-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203050019/https://www.federnuoto.it/home/nuoto/azzurri-nuoto/scheda/340:Benedetta_Pilato.html|archivedate=2019-12-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年，她以14岁6个月的年龄首次出战游泳世锦赛，取代[[费代丽卡·佩莱格里尼|费代丽卡·佩莱格里尼]]成为游泳世锦赛历史上参赛年龄最小的意大利选手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sport.sky.it/altri-sport/2019/07/20/nuoto-speciale-benedetta-pilato-sky-sport|script-title=it:Nuoto, il baby fenomeno Benedetta Pilato: "Ho 14 anni, non mettetemi pressione"|publisher=Sky Sport|date=2019-07-20|accessdate=2020-12-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111005110/https://sport.sky.it/altri-sport/2019/07/20/nuoto-speciale-benedetta-pilato-sky-sport|archivedate=2019-11-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在该届世锦赛期间，她首先在女子50米蛙泳预赛上打破国家纪录，成为首位在该项目上游进30秒的意大利选手<ref>{{cite web |url=https://swimswam.com/14-year-old-benedetta-pilato-becomes-first-italian-woman-sub-30-in-50-breast/ |title=14-Year-Old Benedetta Pilato Becomes First Italian Woman Sub-30 in 50 Breast |work=SwimSwam |date=2019-07-26 |accessdate=2019-07-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101105010/https://swimswam.com/14-year-old-benedetta-pilato-becomes-first-italian-woman-sub-30-in-50-breast/ |archivedate=2020-11-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后，她在同一小项决赛中以30秒的成绩摘银<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lequipe.fr/Natation/Actualites/Championnats-du-monde-lilly-king-conserve-son-titre-sur-le-50-m-brasse-devant-la-jeune-benedetta-pilato/1044425|script-title=fr:Championnats du monde : Lilly King conserve son titre sur le 50 m brasse devant la jeune Benedetta Pilato|publisher=L'Équipe|date=2019-07-28|access-date=2019-07-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203035419/https://www.lequipe.fr/Natation/Actualites/Championnats-du-monde-lilly-king-conserve-son-titre-sur-le-50-m-brasse-devant-la-jeune-benedetta-pilato/1044425|archivedate=2019-12-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

